title: Volleyball Roundup: Northmor falls to Highland
text:
Volleyball Roundup: Northmor falls to Highland Marion Star staff report 9:03 p.m. EDT October 15, 2015 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Highland 3, Northmor 0 
Northmor (12-8, 8-6) lost at Highland 13-25, 12-25, 14-25 Thursday in Mid Ohio Athletic Conference play. For the Knights, Mikayla Briggs had four kills, Anna Donner had three kills and 14 digs, Jordyn Zoll had an ace and 15 assists, Hope Miracle had two blocks and Lindsey Wiseman had 11 digs. 
Seneca East 3, Ridgedale 1 
Host Ridgedale lost to Seneca East 19-25, 20-25, 25-23, 15-25 Thursday in Northern 10 play. Hannah Slane had 33 digs for the Rockets, Rachel Paul had 11 kills and 21 digs, Laney Davis had seven kills and 11 assists, Megan Mulvaine had five kills and Taylor Boyd had nine assists.
